srcset="https://dkri3c1.github.io/p/cyberdefenders-webstrike/image_hu84244ffac105b51ee39aa8616f216009_106333_480x0_resize_box_3.png 480w, https://dkri3c1.github.io/p/cyberdefenders-webstrike/image_hu84244ffac105b51ee39aa8616f216009_106333_1024x0_resize_box_3.png 1024w"
loading="lazy"
class="gallery-image"
data-flex-grow="122"
data-flex-basis="294px"
>&lt;/p>
&lt;p>接下來就看誰是攻擊者ㄌ
