width="1502"
height="590"
srcset="https://dkri3c1.github.io/p/cyberdefenders-webstrike/image-3_hu644746eda2db7ee3c633947624f89409_122826_480x0_resize_box_3.png 480w, https://dkri3c1.github.io/p/cyberdefenders-webstrike/image-3_hu644746eda2db7ee3c633947624f89409_122826_1024x0_resize_box_3.png 1024w"
loading="lazy"
class="gallery-image"
data-flex-grow="254"
data-flex-basis="610px"
>&lt;/p>
&lt;p>&lt;code>ans : Tianjin&lt;/code>&lt;/p>
&lt;h2 id="q2">Q2&lt;/h2>
&lt;p>Knowing the attacker&amp;rsquo;s user-agent assists in creating robust filtering rules. What&amp;rsquo;s the attacker&amp;rsquo;s user agent?&lt;/p>
&lt;hr>
&lt;p>點一個&lt;code>HTTP Protocol&lt;/code>的來看
&lt;img src="https://dkri3c1.github.io/p/cyberdefenders-webstrike/image-4.png"
width="1265"
height="1046"
srcset="https://dkri3c1.github.io/p/cyberdefenders-webstrike/image-4_huc946ca4e4f3de55c289a659503fa1573_78656_480x0_resize_box_3.png 480w, https://dkri3c1.github.io/p/cyberdefenders-webstrike/image-4_huc946ca4e4f3de55c289a659503fa1573_78656_1024x0_resize_box_3.png 1024w"
loading="lazy"
class="gallery-image"
data-flex-grow="120"
data-flex-basis="290px"
>&lt;/p>
&lt;p>&lt;code>ans : Mozilla/5.0 (X11; Linux x86_64; rv:109.0) Gecko/20100101 Firefox/115.0&lt;/code>&lt;/p>
&lt;h2 id="q3">Q3&lt;/h2>
&lt;p>We need to identify if there were potential vulnerabilities exploited. What&amp;rsquo;s the name of the malicious web shell uploaded?&lt;/p>
&lt;hr>
&lt;p>一樣翻一下TCP看攻擊者的攻擊過程&lt;br>
最後在&lt;code>Stream 5&lt;/code>發現了整個犯案過程ww
&lt;img src="https://dkri3c1.github.io/p/cyberdefenders-webstrike/image-5.png"
width="1284"
height="1046"
srcset="https://dkri3c1.github.io/p/cyberdefenders-webstrike/image-5_hufce249aededa4b8206dd68bf23d3dbb7_68393_480x0_resize_box_3.png 480w, https://dkri3c1.github.io/p/cyberdefenders-webstrike/image-5_hufce249aededa4b8206dd68bf23d3dbb7_68393_1024x0_resize_box_3.png 1024w"
loading="lazy"
class="gallery-image"
data-flex-grow="122"
data-flex-basis="294px"
