height="1037"
srcset="https://dkri3c1.github.io/p/cyberdefenders-webstrike/image-7_hu88366addf33990cdd343378bcc4dd69a_89871_480x0_resize_box_3.png 480w, https://dkri3c1.github.io/p/cyberdefenders-webstrike/image-7_hu88366addf33990cdd343378bcc4dd69a_89871_1024x0_resize_box_3.png 1024w"
loading="lazy"
class="gallery-image"
data-flex-grow="123"
data-flex-basis="295px"
>&lt;/p>
&lt;h2 id="q5">Q5&lt;/h2>
&lt;p>Identifying the port utilized by the web shell helps improve firewall configurations for blocking unauthorized outbound traffic. What port was used by the malicious web shell?&lt;/p>
&lt;hr>
&lt;p>在之前的&lt;code>Stream 5&lt;/code>發現攻擊者上傳的webshell，我們可以觀察上面的payload
&lt;img src="https://dkri3c1.github.io/p/cyberdefenders-webstrike/image-6.png"
width="1284"
height="1032"
srcset="https://dkri3c1.github.io/p/cyberdefenders-webstrike/image-6_hu3ed57a61dee33e23ef8fa8c3e79c9ced_73970_480x0_resize_box_3.png 480w, https://dkri3c1.github.io/p/cyberdefenders-webstrike/image-6_hu3ed57a61dee33e23ef8fa8c3e79c9ced_73970_1024x0_resize_box_3.png 1024w"
loading="lazy"
class="gallery-image"
data-flex-grow="124"
data-flex-basis="298px"
>
發現他已&lt;code>8080&lt;/code>這個port當webshell&lt;/p>
&lt;p>&lt;code>ans: 8080&lt;/code>&lt;/p>
&lt;h2 id="q6">Q6&lt;/h2>
&lt;p>Understanding the value of compromised data assists in prioritizing incident response actions. What file was the attacker trying to exfiltrate?&lt;/p>
&lt;hr>
&lt;p>在之前的&lt;code>Stream 13&lt;/code>看到了他&lt;code>RCE&lt;/code>進去之後輸入的指令
&lt;img src="https://dkri3c1.github.io/p/cyberdefenders-webstrike/image-8.png"
width="1272"
height="1042"
srcset="https://dkri3c1.github.io/p/cyberdefenders-webstrike/image-8_hu0c28ab2f952e44c6e559f38d28083db9_109226_480x0_resize_box_3.png 480w, https://dkri3c1.github.io/p/cyberdefenders-webstrike/image-8_hu0c28ab2f952e44c6e559f38d28083db9_109226_1024x0_resize_box_3.png 1024w"
loading="lazy"
class="gallery-image"
data-flex-grow="122"
data-flex-basis="292px"
>
發現他想要去&lt;code>etc/passwd&lt;/code>拿&lt;code>root&lt;/code>的帳號&lt;br>
可是這題只讓我們輸入6個字，所以我想了想就輸入&lt;code>passwd&lt;/code>，然後答案就對ㄌ:D&lt;/p>
&lt;p>&lt;code>ans : passwd&lt;/code>&lt;/p>
&lt;h2 id="後記">後記&lt;/h2>
&lt;p>數位鑑識好玩:D&lt;/p></description></item><item><title>Cyberdefenders - OpenWire</title><link>https://dkri3c1.github.io/p/cyberdefenders-openwire/</link><pubDate>Wed, 07 Feb 2024 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://dkri3c1.github.io/p/cyberdefenders-openwire/</guid><description>&lt;img src="https://dkri3c1.github.io/p/cyberdefenders-openwire/cover.png" alt="Featured image of post Cyberdefenders - OpenWire" />&lt;h2 id="q1">Q1&lt;/h2>
&lt;p>By identifying the C2 IP, we can block traffic to and from this IP, helping to contain the breach and prevent further data exfiltration or command execution. Can you provide the IP of the C2 server that communicated with our server?&lt;/p>
&lt;hr>
&lt;p>要找出攻擊者的ip我們可以用&lt;code>Endpoint&lt;/code>觀察
&lt;img src="https://dkri3c1.github.io/p/cyberdefenders-openwire/image-5.png"
width="1906"
height="704"
