&lt;p>Following up on the previous question, what is the name of the service found to be vulnerable?&lt;/p>
&lt;hr>
&lt;p>撈了很久的Wireshark還是沒找到，最後想說去看看&lt;code>61616&lt;/code>這個port到底在幹嘛
