&lt;h2 id="q4">Q4&lt;/h2>
&lt;p>The attacker&amp;rsquo;s infrastructure often involves multiple components. What is the IP of the second C2 server?&lt;/p>
&lt;hr>
&lt;p>觀察一下被駭的server有沒有傳送東西給其他陌生的ip 發現確實有
&lt;img src="https://dkri3c1.github.io/p/cyberdefenders-openwire/image-9.png"
width="1920"
height="219"
srcset="https://dkri3c1.github.io/p/cyberdefenders-openwire/image-9_hu3aa5ce7f7b946f3659dd29cb1d44b4e8_34543_480x0_resize_box_3.png 480w, https://dkri3c1.github.io/p/cyberdefenders-openwire/image-9_hu3aa5ce7f7b946f3659dd29cb1d44b4e8_34543_1024x0_resize_box_3.png 1024w"
