&lt;h2 id="後記">後記&lt;/h2>
&lt;p>基本上快一年多沒有碰wireshark這個鬼東西ㄌ(雖然前陣子T貓的時候有稍微玩一下)，感覺好不熟悉QAQ，希望我能透過練習上面的Lab讓我在分區的時候藍隊不會死那麼慘。&lt;/p></description></item><item><title>SCAICT Winter_Camp_2024</title><link>https://dkri3c1.github.io/p/scaict-winter_camp_2024/</link><pubDate>Wed, 24 Jan 2024 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://dkri3c1.github.io/p/scaict-winter_camp_2024/</guid><description>&lt;img src="https://dkri3c1.github.io/p/scaict-winter_camp_2024/cover.jpg" alt="Featured image of post SCAICT Winter_Camp_2024" />&lt;h2 id="前言">前言&lt;/h2>
